<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Updating... | Jadeedskills</title>
    <style>
        body {
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 650px;
            background: white;
            padding: 50px 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        /* Under Construction Icon Animation */
        .icon {
            font-size: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
            animation: wrench 2.5s ease infinite;
        }

        @keyframes wrench {
            0%, 100% { transform: rotate(-12deg); }
            50% { transform: rotate(12deg); }
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .name {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #007bff;
        }

        .brand {
            color: #007bff;
        }

        /* Progress Bar Animation */
        .progress-container {
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .progress-bar {
            width: 70%;
            height: 8px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            animation: loading 2s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes loading {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(150%); }
        }

        .pulse {
            animation: pulse-animation 2s infinite;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-animation {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.4; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
        <h1>
            I am <span class="name">SYED DANIYAL</span> from <span class="brand">Jadeedskills</span>, 
            <br>
            Please come back after a very small time. We are currently <strong>updating and redesigning</strong> our website for you.
        </h1>

        <div class="progress-container">
            <div class="progress-bar"></div>
        </div>

        <p class="pulse">Working on something awesome...</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px; font-weight: bold;">Thanks for your cooperation!</p>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
